para_trans: Regarding the grant of fata approval of the first director and members of the Institute for registration under the Companies Act, 2023 of the autonomous institute Vasantrao Naik Research and Training Institute (Vanati).
Other Backward Classes Bahujan Welfare Department,
Government Decision Number: MAHAJYO-2025 / Q. No.44 / Institution
Madam Kama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,
Reference: 1) Government Decision Other Backward Classes Bahujan Welfare Department, No. MAHAJYO-2023 / Q. No.38 / Institution, dated 8/10/2024.
2) Other Backward Classes Bahujan Welfare Department, Office Order, No.Majyoi-2025 / P.No.44 Institutions, D. December 16, 2025

Introduction: - In the context of the above. The Government of India has approved the establishment of Vasantrao Naik Research and Training Institute (VANARTY), an autonomous institute under Rule 8 of the Companies Act, 2013, at Mumbai, to focus on the socio-economic and educational development of Vimukt Jati-A, Vimukt Jati-B, Vimukt Jati-C and Vimukt Jati-D, including the Gor Banjara tribe, and to carry out various programmes / activities for students, youth and other candidates belonging to these communities. Say "FATE! "Power to take such decisions as may be necessary from time to time in connection with the establishment and functioning of the institution. Ministers (Other Backward Bahujan Welfare Department) have been provided.

As per the provision in the Government Decision dated 08.10.2024, the matter of appointment of "First Director and Member as representative of the Government to form a One Party" for registration of Vasantrao Naik Research and Training Institute (One Party) under Section 8 of the Companies Act, 2013 was under consideration of the Government.

Government Decision: - The following office bearers / officers are being appointed by the Government as "First Directors" for registration of Vasantrao Naik Research and Training Institute (VANARTI) under Section 8 of the Companies Act, 2013.

para_trans: Government Decision Number: MAHAJYO-2025 / Q. No.44 / Institution

The Managing Director, Vasantrao Naik Research and Training Institute (VANARTY), is being authorised to complete all the necessary procedures for registration of "Vasantrao Naik Research and Training Institute (VANARTY)" as aforesaid under Section 8 of the Companies Act, 2013, compile the information and particulars of all the directors and members, take their signatures along with the necessary documents, etc.
Since the company is owned by the Government, ex-officio members / directors mentioned in the following table are being appointed as representatives of the Government.

4. RIA Paragraph No. Appropriate decision shall be taken at the first meeting of the Board of Directors of One Party in respect of the appointment of the office bearers / officers as directors, in addition to the person who shall be the first to register the Mahajyoti Institute as a director, as mentioned in section 1.
The entity shall come into existence from the date of its actual registration under the Companies Act.
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
